divs: Sighting DetailsSaw the lights late this time... 1st light disappeared in a second ..2nd light did the same 3 seconds later. Sky was clear. there was no turn of a jet's landing lights as I have seen near O'Hare in St. Charles. I was thinking that Jupiter was in the sky tonight, but it is in the west tonight. It looked like there was a planet with another kicked in for flavor like Saturn or Mercury. they just disappeared!!! DE JA VUE?
Summary: saw the same thing 3-5 years ago at this location!
